                "invention-title": [
                    "Ship cleaning system and method based on clean energy",
                    "一种基于清洁能源的船舶清洗系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a ship cleaning system and method based on clean energy. The cleaning system comprises a power generation system, a hydrogen production system, an energy storage system, a steam generation system, a cleaning system, a cleaning visualization system, a seawater circulation system and a control system. Hydrogen can be produced and stored through wind power or photovoltaic power generation, high-temperature and high-pressure saturated steam is produced through the hydrogen, the high-temperature and high-speed saturated steam flow is jetted to the surface of a ship body, double cleaning of mechanical stripping and high-temperature killing of organisms attached to the ship body is achieved, and through regular cleaning, the cleaning efficiency is improved. The ship body surface smoothness is improved while ship body finish paint is protected, the navigational speed is increased while ship oil consumption is reduced, the service life of the ship body is prolonged, the ship maintenance cost and time cost are reduced, the ship cleaning device is friendly to the marine environment, and the cleaning device flexible in place can be provided."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种基于清洁能源的船舶清洗系统及方法，所述清洗系统包括发电系统、制氢系统、储能系统、蒸汽发生系统、清洗系统、清洗可视化系统、海水循环系统和控制系统。本发明的目的在于提供能够通过风力或光伏发电生产并储存氢气，利用氢气生产高温高压饱和蒸汽，通过将高温、高速饱和蒸汽流喷射于船体表面，实现对船体附着生物的机械剥离和高温杀灭的双重清洗，通过定期清洗，显著降低船体附着物生长概率，保护船体面漆的同时提升船体表面光滑度，降低船舶油耗的同时提升航速，提升船体寿命，降低船舶维护保养的费用成本和时间成本，对海洋环境友好，能够提供地点灵活的清洗装置。"
                }
            ]
